reviewText: Didn't know it was the video that you need the bag for disappointed wanted the regular one

This is a great video if you want to get fit. I couldn't even make it all the way through this video. Of course I haven't exercised for 20 years. Billy really knows his stuff. I now have his complete library and love each time I exercise. I would recommend this tape and all of Billy Balnks workouts.

This is not like your regular TAE BO dvd's, I did not enjoy it, and didn't feel like I got a nice energetic workout.  I should note I did not buy the punching bag, my husband and I just shadow boxed, but I just feel like TAE BO is known for heart pumping cardio, and this should be more like a nap with a few punches.
